@startuml
title 体积与土方量计算（复杂度 O(n²))

actor 工程师 as user
participant "前端" as front
participant "Gateway" as gw
participant "zrws-process" as svc
participant "Python AI" as ai
database "MySQL" as db

== 体积计算 ==
user -> front: 框选目标区域 + 设置基准面
front -> gw: POST /api/v1/processing/volume
gw -> svc: 转发
svc -> db: [SQL] SELECT t_elevation_result WHERE mission_id={id}
svc -> ai: [gRPC] calculateVolume(dsm, roi, baseElevation)
ai -> ai: 1. ROI 裁剪 DSM
ai -> ai: 2. 基准面以上 → 挖方体积
ai -> ai: 3. 基准面以下 → 填方体积
ai -> ai: 4. 网格积分法精度估算
ai -> ai: 5. 生成截面剖面图
ai --> svc: VolumeResult{ cutVolume, fillVolume, netVolume, accuracyPercent, profileImageUrl }
svc -> db: [SQL] INSERT t_volume_calc
svc --> gw: R<VolumeResultVO>
gw --> front: 挖方/填方/净方量 + 剖面图

== 两期对比 ==
user -> front: 选择两期 DSM 对比
front -> gw: POST /api/v1/processing/volume/diff
gw -> svc: 转发
svc -> ai: [gRPC] diffVolume(dsm1, dsm2)
ai -> ai: 两期 DSM 逐像素差值
ai -> ai: 差值积分 → 总变化体积
ai --> svc: DiffVolumeResult{ changeVolume, changeHeatmapUrl }
svc --> gw: R<DiffVolumeResultVO>
gw --> front: 变化热力图 + 体积变化量

@enduml
